text: Welcome to 'Getting Started with Python'. In this one-hour introductory lecture, we will first explore how to install Python on different operating systems.
Then, we will set up a development environment, and finally, we will write our first Python script.

This session aims to provide you with a solid foundation in Python, ensuring you understand the installation process, how to set up a comfortable coding environment, and how to write and execute a basic Python script. By the end, you should feel confident in starting your Python coding journey.
